Description: The Bessed Virgin to SIster Pierina in Montichiari,
  Italy, 1947
---
Our Lord, my Divine Son. is tired of being greatly offended by men
through sins against holy purity. He is inclined to command a deluge
of retribution. I have interceded in order that he may still exercise
mercy. I therefore request prayers and penance in reparation for those
sins.
